     <div class=\"tcs-b2-tile-body\">\n              <div class=\"tcs-b2-tile-top\">\n                <span class=\"tcs-b2-kicker\">Transparency</span>\n                <span class=\"tcs-b2-arrow\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\u2192</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"tcs-b2-tile-title\">Complaints & Transparency</div>\n              <div class=\"tcs-b2-tile-sub\">How we handle disputes, updates, and corrections</div>\n            </div>\n          </a>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- RIGHT: \u201cBUILT FOR PLAYERS\u201d -->\n      <div class=\"tcs-b2-right\" aria-label=\"Why Top Casino Scout is built for players\">\n        <div class=\"tcs-b2-panel\">\n          <h2 class=\"tcs-b2-title\">Why Top Casino Scout is built for players</h2>\n\n          <p class=\"tcs-b2-copy\">\n            Most bonus pages exist to push a click. We built Top Casino Scout to reduce mistakes\u2014especially the expensive ones.\n            That means prioritising eligibility reality, terms that affect withdrawals, and the risk signals that rarely appear in marketing copy.\n          </p>\n\n          <ul class=\"tcs-b2-bullets\">\n            <li><strong>Verification-first checks</strong> to help you avoid time-wasters and higher-risk operators.</li>\n            <li><strong>Plain-English terms</strong> that focus on what actually changes value (wagering, caps, exclusions, withdrawal rules).</li>\n            <li><strong>Evidence-led standards</strong> designed to be scrutinised, with stated policies and reproducible logic.</li>\n            <li><strong>Player-outcome focus</strong> that highlights KYC friction, payout constraints, and common failure points.</li>\n          </ul>\n\n          <div class=\"tcs-b2-seo\">\n            <h3 class=\"tcs-b2-mini\">What makes a \u201cgood bonus\u201d actually good?</h3>\n            <p class=\"tcs-b2-copy\">\n              A strong offer is not just a headline number. Real value comes from the rules behind it: how quickly you can clear wagering,\n              whether games contribute fairly, and whether withdrawals are realistic once you\u2019ve met the requirements. Top Casino Scout is built\n              to help you compare casino bonuses using practical checks and player-first standards\u2014so you can spot value, avoid bad terms, and\n              make better decisions with less guesswork.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  #tcs-section-b{\n    padding: 62px 0 76px;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-wrap{\n    max-width: 1680px;\n    margin-left: auto;\n    margin-right: auto;\n    padding-left: 24px;\n    padding-right: 24px;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-grid{\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 18px;\n    align-items: start;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-title{\n    margin: 0 0 10px;\n    font-weight: 950;\n    letter-spacing: .01em;\n    color: #ffcc33;\n    font-family: Oswald, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(20px, 1.75vw, 28px);\n    line-height: 1.15;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-sub{\n    margin: 0 0 18px;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,.86);\n    line-height: 1.55;\n    max-width: 62ch;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-tiles{\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 12px;\n    margin-top: 12px;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-tile{\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 12px;\n    align-items: center;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    background: var(--tcs-surface);\n    border: 1px solid var(--tcs-border);\n    border-radius: 14px;\n    box-shadow: var(--tcs-shadow-soft);\n    transition: transform .15s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, border-color .2s ease, opacity .2s ease;\n    color: var(--tcs-text);\n    padding: 14px 14px;\n    min-height: 86px;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-tile:hover{\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow: var(--tcs-shadow-card);\n    border-color: var(--tcs-border-strong);\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-tile-media{\n    width: 56px;\n    height: 56px;\n    border-radius: 14px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--tcs-border);\n    background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(31,170,89,.16), rgba(5,5,27,0));\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    color: var(--tcs-green-500);\n    box-shadow: var(--tcs-shadow-soft);\n    flex: 0 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-tile-body{ min-width: 0; flex: 1 1 auto; }\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-tile-top{\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    gap: 10px;\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-kicker{\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: .12em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: var(--tcs-soft);\n    font-weight: 900;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-arrow{\n    opacity: .9;\n    color: var(--tcs-text);\n    font-weight: 900;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-tile-title{\n    font-weight: 950;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    text-overflow: ellipsis;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-tile-sub{\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,.82);\n    line-height: 1.35;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    text-overflow: ellipsis;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-panel{\n    background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(31,170,89,.12) 0%, rgba(5,5,27,0) 55%), var(--tcs-surface);\n    border: 1px solid var(--tcs-border);\n    border-radius: 18px;\n    box-shadow: var(--tcs-shadow-card);\n    padding: 18px 18px 16px;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-copy{\n    margin: 0 0 14px;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,.90);\n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-bullets{\n    margin: 0 0 14px;\n    padding-left: 18px;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,.92);\n    line-height: 1.65;\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-bullets li{ margin: 8px 0; }\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-bullets strong{ color: rgba(255,255,255,.98); }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-seo{\n    margin-top: 14px;\n    padding-top: 14px;\n    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\n  }\n\n  #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-mini{\n    margin: 0 0 8px;\n    font-weight: 950;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,.96);\n    letter-spacing: .01em;\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 980px){\n    #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-wrap{\n      max-width: 1100px;\n      padding-left: 16px;\n      padding-right: 16px;\n    }\n    #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-grid{\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n    #tcs-section-b .tcs-b2-tiles{\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n\n\n<!-- TRUST + METHODOLOGY SNAPSHOT (SECTION 4) \u2014 TCS WARDROBE v2 DARK (UPGRADED COPY) -->\n<section class=\"tcs-section tcs-section--dark\" id=\"tcs-trust\">\n  <div class=\"tcs-container\">\n\n    <div class=\"tcs-trust-head\">\n      <h2 class=\"tcs-heading-lg\">Why Players Trust TopCasinoScout</h2>\n\n      <p class=\"tcs-text-lead tcs-text-lead--narrow\">\n        TopCasinoScout is built for adults who want clearer, safer guidance in a high-risk, regulated category.\n        We focus on the details that affect real outcomes after sign-up\u2014licensing context, withdrawal conditions, KYC friction,\n        bonus mechanics, and player protection signals\u2014so readers can make calmer, better-informed decisions.\n      </p>\n\n      <p class=\"tcs-trust-sublead\">\n        Our aim is simple: less hype, more scrutiny. Where terms are unclear, enforcement looks one-sided, or support practices raise concerns,\n        we flag it openly and steer readers toward safer alternatives.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tcs-trust-grid\">\n\n      <!-- LEFT: TRUST PILLARS -->\n      <div class=\"tcs-trust-left\">\n\n        <div class=\"tcs-trust-cards\">\n\n          <article class=\"tcs-trust-card\">\n            <div class=\"tcs-trust-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M12 2l8 4v6c0 5-3.5 9-8 10C7.5 21 4 17 4 12V6l8-4z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                <path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n              </svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"tcs-trust-title\">Licensed, accountable operators</h3>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-text\">\n              We prioritise operators that present clear licensing and jurisdiction context, along with transparent ownership and enforceable terms.\n              If a casino\u2019s fundamentals look weak\u2014vague licensing claims, unclear rules, or shifting conditions\u2014we treat that as a material risk signal.\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-mini\">\n              Reader outcome: fewer surprises, stronger accountability when something goes wrong.\n            </p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"tcs-trust-card\">\n            <div class=\"tcs-trust-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M12 1v6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M12 17v6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M1 12h6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M17 12h6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M4.2 4.2l4.2 4.2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M15.6 15.6l4.2 4.2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M4.2 19.8l4.2-4.2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M15.6 8.4l4.2-4.2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n              </svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"tcs-trust-title\">Withdrawal reality, not marketing</h3>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-text\">\n              Most \u201ctop lists\u201d talk bonuses. Players care about withdrawals. We surface the practical constraints that decide whether funds move smoothly:\n              processing expectations, limits, payment method restrictions, common bottlenecks, and whether terms are framed fairly in practice.\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-mini\">\n              Reader outcome: clearer expectations around cash-out, verification, and delays.\n            </p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"tcs-trust-card\">\n            <div class=\"tcs-trust-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M7 11V8a5 5 0 0110 0v3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M6 11h12v10H6V11z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M12 15v3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n              </svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"tcs-trust-title\">KYC & verification clarity</h3>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-text\">\n              KYC is where many players get stuck\u2014often at the point they try to withdraw. We explain typical verification triggers, what documentation is commonly requested,\n              and the friction points that turn \u201cquick cash-out\u201d promises into long waits.\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-mini\">\n              Reader outcome: fewer verification surprises, faster resolution when checks appear.\n            </p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"tcs-trust-card\">\n            <div class=\"tcs-trust-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M6 19c4-8 8-12 14-14-2 6-6 10-14 14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M8 16l-3 3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n              </svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"tcs-trust-title\">Bonus terms decoded, country-aware</h3>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-text\">\n              We break down the terms that change the real value of an offer: wagering requirements, game exclusions, max cash-out caps,\n              time windows, minimum deposit rules, and \u201cdiscretionary\u201d clauses that can affect outcomes. We also emphasise that eligibility and\n              payment options vary by country, state, or province\u2014so readers should always confirm local rules.\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-mini\">\n              Reader outcome: clearer bonus value, fewer avoidable rule breaches, better fit by region.\n            </p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"tcs-trust-card\">\n            <div class=\"tcs-trust-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M4 7h16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M4 12h16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n                <path d=\"M4 17h10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n              </svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"tcs-trust-title\">Independent, player-first editorial stance</h3>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-text\">\n              TopCasinoScout is free to use. Some links may be affiliate links, but operators cannot buy favourable assessments, higher placement,\n              or a better verdict. We surface the critical information early\u2014wagering, min deposits, caps, exclusions, and enforcement language\u2014so readers can judge risk quickly.\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-mini\">\n              Reader outcome: clearer decisions, less bias, and fewer \u201cfine print\u201d surprises.\n            </p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"tcs-trust-card\">\n            <div class=\"tcs-trust-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n                <path d=\"M12 3c4 0 7 3 7 7 0 5-7 11-7 11S5 15 5 10c0-4 3-7 7-7z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                <path d=\"M12 10.5a2.5 2.5 0 100-5 2.5 2.5 0 000 5z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n              </svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"tcs-trust-title\">Responsible gambling & safer play signals</h3>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-text\">\n              We encourage readers to treat limits, time-outs, and self-exclusion as normal safety tools. If gambling stops being enjoyable,\n              the safest choice may be to pause and seek support. We aim to signpost safer-gambling guidance throughout our content, especially on high-intent pages.\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-mini\">\n              Reader outcome: more control, fewer impulsive decisions, better use of safety tools.\n            </p>\n          </article>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- RIGHT: METHODOLOGY SNAPSHOT + CTAs -->\n      <aside class=\"tcs-trust-right\">\n\n        <div class=\"tcs-trust-panel\">\n          <div class=\"tcs-trust-panel-top\">\n            <div class=\"tcs-trust-panel-badge\" aria-label=\"Methodology snapshot\">\n              <span class=\"tcs-trust-panel-dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span class=\"tcs-trust-panel-badge-text\">TRUST & METHOD</span>\n            </div>\n\n            <h3 class=\"tcs-heading-md\">What we check before we recommend anything</h3>\n\n            <ul class=\"tcs-trust-list\">\n              <li><strong>Licensing & jurisdiction:</strong> who regulates the operator, and where the rules apply.</li>\n              <li><strong>Withdrawals & payments:</strong> practical constraints, limits, and common friction points.</li>\n              <li><strong>KYC triggers:</strong> when verification appears and how it impacts cash-out.</li>\n              <li><strong>Bonus enforcement:</strong> wagering, exclusions, caps, time limits, and discretionary clauses.</li>\n              <li><strong>Player protection:</strong> safeguards, support behaviour, and red-flag patterns.</li>\n            </ul>\n\n            <p class=\"tcs-trust-note\">\n              18+ only. Eligibility varies by region. Always check local laws, terms, and payment availability before registering or depositing.\n            </p>\n\n            <div class=\"tcs-trust-microgrid\">\n              <a class=\"tcs-trust-miniCard\" href=\"/how-we-rate-online-casinos/\">\n                <span class=\"tcs-trust-miniCard-title\">Rating methodology</span>\n                <span class=\"tcs-trust-miniCard-sub\">How we assess risk & value</span>\n              </a>\n              <a class=\"tcs-trust-miniCard\" href=\"/complaints-transparency-report/\">\n                <span class=\"tcs-trust-miniCard-title\">Transparency report</span>\n                <span class=\"tcs-trust-miniCard-sub\">What we track & disclose</span>\n              </a>\n              <a class=\"tcs-trust-miniCard\" href=\"/af